org.apache.http.client.methods

接口 CloseableHttpResponse

  • 所有超级接口:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable, HttpMessage, HttpResponse

    public interface CloseableHttpResponse
extends HttpResponse, Closeable
    Extended version of the HttpResponse interface that also extends Closeable.
    从以下版本开始:
    4.3

      • 从接口继承的方法 org.apache.http.HttpResponse
